---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout
  title="Projects | Xianglong Tao"
  description="Open source projects and experiments in systems design and equilibrium analysis"
>
  <div class="projects">
    <h1>Projects</h1>
    <p class="intro">
      Open source projects exploring systems design, equilibrium analysis,
      and practical applications of stability theory.
    </p>

    <div class="project-list">
      <article class="project">
        <h2>
          <a href="https://github.com/daidaitaotao/taocore" target="_blank">TaoCore</a>
        </h2>
        <p class="tagline">
          Systems-level abstraction layer for stability and coherence analysis
        </p>
        <p class="description">
          TaoCore provides equilibrium-based convergence detection for iterative AI systems.
          Instead of arbitrary <code>for i in range(10)</code> loops, it offers principled
          stopping criteria with oscillation detection, stability scoring, and explicit
          failure modes.
        </p>
        <div class="tech-stack">
          <span>Python</span>
          <span>NumPy</span>
          <span>Graph Theory</span>
        </div>
        <div class="links">
          <a href="https://github.com/daidaitaotao/taocore" target="_blank">GitHub</a>
          <a href="https://pypi.org/project/taocore/" target="_blank">PyPI</a>
          <a href="https://github.com/daidaitaotao/taocore#readme" target="_blank">Docs</a>
        </div>
        <div class="status">
          <span class="badge">v0.1.0</span>
          <span class="badge">Published</span>
          <span class="badge">115 tests</span>
        </div>
      </article>

      <article class="project placeholder">
        <h2>Future Projects</h2>
        <p class="description">
          More explorations in systems design, equilibrium analysis, and practical
          applications coming soon.
        </p>
      </article>
    </div>
  </div>
</Layout>

<style>
  .projects {
    max-width: 800px;
  }

  h1 {
    font-size: 2.5rem;
    font-weight: 600;
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
    line-height: 1.2;
  }

  .intro {
    color: #7f8c8d;
    line-height: 1.7;
    margin-bottom: 3rem;
    font-size: 1.05rem;
  }

  .project-list {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 3rem;
  }

  .project {
    border: 1px solid #e1e8ed;
    border-radius: 8px;
    padding: 2rem;
    background: #fafbfc;
  }

  .project.placeholder {
    opacity: 0.6;
  }

  .project h2 {
    font-size: 1.75rem;
    margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
    margin-top: 0;
  }

  .project h2 a {
    color: #3498db;
    text-decoration: none;
    transition: color 0.2s;
  }

  .project h2 a:hover {
    color: #2980b9;
  }

  .tagline {
    font-weight: 500;
    color: #2c3e50;
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
    font-size: 1.05rem;
  }

  .description {
    color: #7f8c8d;
    line-height: 1.7;
    margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
  }

  .description code {
    font-family: 'SF Mono', 'Monaco', 'Inconsolata', 'Fira Mono', monospace;
    background: #f4f5f7;
    padding: 0.15rem 0.4rem;
    border-radius: 3px;
    font-size: 0.9em;
    color: #2c3e50;
  }

  .tech-stack {
    display: flex;
    flex-wrap: wrap;
    gap: 0.5rem;
    margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
  }

  .tech-stack span {
    background: #ecf0f1;
    color: #7f8c8d;
    padding: 0.25rem 0.75rem;
    border-radius: 4px;
    font-size: 0.85rem;
    font-weight: 500;
  }

  .links {
    display: flex;
    gap: 1.5rem;
    margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
  }

  .links a {
    color: #3498db;
    text-decoration: none;
    font-weight: 500;
    transition: color 0.2s;
  }

  .links a:hover {
    color: #2980b9;
    text-decoration: underline;
  }

  .status {
    display: flex;
    gap: 0.75rem;
    padding-top: 1.5rem;
    border-top: 1px solid #e1e8ed;
  }

  .badge {
    background: #e8f4f8;
    color: #3498db;
    padding: 0.25rem 0.75rem;
    border-radius: 4px;
    font-size: 0.85rem;
    font-weight: 500;
  }

  @media (max-width: 640px) {
    h1 {
      font-size: 2rem;
    }

    .project {
      padding: 1.5rem;
    }

    .links {
      flex-direction: column;
      gap: 0.75rem;
    }

    .status {
      flex-wrap: wrap;
    }
  }
</style>
